Usage: octoqlgen schema [flags]

Materialize or verify a pinned GraphQL schema.

Flags:
  -h, --help                      Show context-sensitive help.
      --version                   Show version information.

      --config=PATH               Path to an octoql configuration file. Defaults
                                  to octoql.yaml.
  -o, --output=PATH               Write the exact schema bytes to a file instead
                                  of stdout.
      --github-version=VERSION    Fetch a pinned github/docs schema version
                                  (fpt, ghec, or ghes-X.Y).
      --source-url=URL            Fetch a schema from an immutable URL.
      --revision=SHA              Full github/docs commit revision for
                                  --github-version.
      --sha256=HEX                Expected SHA-256 for a direct remote source.
